caption.p: Distribution of the differences between the week of peak incidence for two influenza virus types. ( A) Comparison of the peak timing for influenza A/H1N1 versus A/H3N2 (peak epidemic week of A/H3N2 minus that of A/H1N1). ( B) Comparison of the peak timing for influenza B versus A/H1N1 (peak epidemic week of A/H1N1 minus that B). ( C) Comparison of the peak timing for influenza B versus A/H3N2 (peak epidemic week of A/H3N2 minus that of B).
